{"type": "article", "id": 29972, "title": "这盏柔软的“窗帘灯”想为你模仿阳光的感觉｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-07-21T23:01:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 30475, "name": "Atelier I-N-D-J"}, {"id": 30476, "name": "Sotterranea Officina Sperimentale"}, {"id": 30477, "name": "Dear Human"}, {"id": 30478, "name": "Anson Calder"}, {"id": 30479, "name": "Jeeyoung Yang"}, {"id": 30480, "name": "Siyu Lou"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 69, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160804170756UeVO3cTziZAqfEyx.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Triangle Step Ladder by Jeeyoung Yang</h3><p>不少人会在家中备着一把梯子，但它们的造型往往更适合摆在建筑工地，缺少了一股居家的气息，设计师 <a href=\"http://www.jeeyoungyang.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jeeyoung Yang</a> 希望通过这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.jeeyoungyang.com/#/triangle/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Triangle Step</a> 的三角梯改变人们对梯子的刻板印象。梯子的造型非常简洁，平时以 2D 平面状态挂在墙上，看上去像是一件装饰品，可以很好地融入室内环境当中。使用时只需要调整可旋转的金属支架就能转变成 3D 结构，美中不足之处在于两层胡桃木制作而成的踏板距离地面分别为 17.78 和 30.48 厘米，可以提升的高度有限。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004151R7fulmUCzH1p5ZFB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.481667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004151zXGLjCUVunRAxvr8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.594531\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004151O0RUCTzrVykt9BY5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.188333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004151GrEnYDeohxfvbHJq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.186667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Plump Thonet by Atelier I-N-D-J</h3><p>维也纳知名家具公司 Gebrüder Thonet 生产过不少经典的家具设计，其中大受欢迎的 No. 18 椅在 1859 至 1930 年之间就累计生产了五千万把。设计工作室 <a href=\"http://www.i-n-d-j.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Atelier I-N-D-J</a> 最近就为这款拥有 150 年历史的经典产品进行了一番重新设计，将其命名为 <a href=\"http://design.i-n-d-j.com/PLUMP-THONET\" rel=\"nofollow\">Plump Thonet</a>。新款座椅增加了柔软舒适的黑色皮革坐垫，上面整齐排列了 16 个铜制圆孔以用来确定椅腿的位置，同时保留了经典造型的黑色椅背也由这些圆孔固定。一根纤细的铜制扶手从坐垫一侧延伸，穿过椅背连接起了两种不同的元素，带给人一种奇妙的视觉效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004121f2IuzY1BndaO8SPc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561458\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004121efw9nHD4Pc6TYOoA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004121gBEvqeC9Q1acVbn7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004120nvoXC9p2P5a3684j.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"2.061458\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004121dU25MXbpocx1KTer.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sostanza by Sotterranea Officina Sperimentale</h3><p>和其他书写工具相比，别出心裁的铅笔设计似乎有些少见。来自意大利的 Sotterranea Officina Sperimentale 工作室最近推出了一款名为 Sostanza 的铅笔，不管是造型还是功能都让人颇为惊艳。这些铅笔都采用精选自世界各地的天然木材，以手工制作的方式在意大利进行小批量生产。铅笔本身仅由重量极轻的笔套和用来固定的圆环两部分组成，外形采用了符合人体工程学的设计，带给人流畅的书写体验。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1417483388/sostanza\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 25 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004050aPg7LwXudVWRAm0l.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607220040503Da0Qf8ivntCGHwk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004051bojpe7ak0vSX5h9w.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004052kliyMT0wV8xdYEAK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004050riNHOJv8E4mQdXsq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.799511\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607220040518DfSGynOKrU5lp1h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.677262\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Window by Siyu Lou</h3><p>即便是在没有窗户的房间，你同样能用氛围灯模拟出穿过窗户的阳光了。今天要介绍的这款壁灯 Window 是 Siyu Lou 的设计作品，它不仅可以为无窗的小房间提供温暖的灯光，将数个组合在一起后还能作为装饰使用。壁灯内置了一张能够灵活调节的 LED 灯板，只要轻轻一拉，就会像窗帘一样降下，倾泻出温暖的光芒。在家里挂上这么一张不是用来遮挡光线的“窗帘”，还挺有趣的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607220040239BTjZSslJImwMopz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607220040233ojO4zIDrYnlfFiV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004023vGJOjnu8lVoeQUkW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004023sJTj5NbBhdKWoVX3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.443810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004023auUz1g4st3VopxiS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.608571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722004023PhHD8iBoM9baGRA1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Sweet Seat by Dear Human</h3><p>对于经常搬家或者是在两地奔波的人来说，拥有一件可以应对不同需求的家具就显得非常重要了。<a href=\"http://www.dearhuman.ca/projects-2/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dear Human</a> 工作室推出的这款多功能沙发 <a href=\"http://www.dearhuman.ca/projects/sweet-seat/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sweet Seat</a> 就是设计师们根据个人经验而设计的，外形简单却不失功能性。它由五个大小不一的坐垫组成，通过橡皮圈固定在一起，看起来像是放大的礼物盒。只需要将坐垫拆开后重新排布，沙发就能转变为一张舒适的床铺。Sweet Seat 的配色走的是低调温和的风格，适用于各种室内环境，不会带来突兀的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003954fFOn9307XWrcygjH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003955kqJPwU0Qn6B5gvNu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666250\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003954rF1SIb3hf5twGDMz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003955kDCWAaF4gnITKPuz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.683333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003954P6IlqnXF21cBZYNz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Anson Calder bag system by Anson Calder</h3><p>在卖手提包这件事上，纽约品牌 <a href=\"http://ansoncalder.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Anson Calder</a> 走的是不常见的定制化路线：在选择了手提包的款式之后，顾客可以从一系列为特定物品量身定制的配件中进行挑选，通过包内六条固定带将它们像口袋一样和手提包“缝合”起来，打造出独一无二的收纳空间。丰富的配件选择是这套定制系统的一大特色，除了手机壳、笔套等常用的小配件之外，雨伞袋、公文夹以及各尺寸的数码产品包应有尽有。无论是配件还是手提包都采用来自法国的小牛皮革精心打造，缝线则来自知名的德国品牌 Gutermann。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/59107441/anson-calder-bags-and-cases-customizable-access-w\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，单个手提包的价格为 560 美元，搭配四个配件后的价格为 940 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003934Cf8kanGBEJR7hwpS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003936kij9Co4maSGsMEhv.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003934PcD9uCLktAKW2OHF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.447059\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607220039348TaSC6m1tHVJbDr4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.975398\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003934LGtfkjEKp1AODmTg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.989943\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160722003934KrRHyYjwp93gzsa8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.884993\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}